About:
Juggernaut powers On Demand Technology platforms for entrepreneurs and enterprise level
initiatives.
Our IP is a robust backend infrastructure which is structured in form of modules
geared towards scheduling, dispatching/tracking, payment, matching, allocation and some
other core functionalities. These modules help us cater to diverse business models in the
On­Demand space. Typical implementation involves plumbing of the modules to create
custom front end mobile apps, dashboards and analytics panels.
In the past 6 months, we have deployed more than 15 on­demand platforms that have
altogether completed more than 300,000 transactions.
